          action
        </p>
        <p>
          For more info please check the components's official{" "}
          <a
            target="_blank"
            className="kt-link"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            href="https://material-ui.com/components/chips/"
          >
            demos & documentation
          </a>
        </p>
      </Notice>

